name: Spring Fashionista Dress Up
description:
Like being aware of the latest fashion?
Now let princess Ellie dress with the best of spring fashion. She loves bright colors, choose cute dresses and many accessories that every girl should wear.
There are a variety of outfits to combine as you like.

- 29 dresses
- 36 blouses and poles
- Many hairstyles, pants, skirts and accessories

You want to be a fashion designer?
Use your creativity to put together the best combinations.

Be a fashionista and have fun with our dress up games for girls.

Princesses dress up games!
